						               													<description>In a violent cyberpunk universe, players take on the role of coaches to lead teams of 4 players with the goal of becoming the best team in the Neon League.&amp;#10;A 1vs1 board game that simulates the rules of rugby. Tackles, blows, players on the ground, injuries and all kinds of situations that make takkure a fast-paced and fun game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Immerse yourself in this universe and play for victory!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play:&amp;#10;Takkure is a metal miniature game based on the rules of rugby. Players must land the ball in the opposing try zone to score a point. For this, they can only pass the ball to a player behind them, and the defense can only tackle the ball carrier.&amp;#10;The game board measures 46x68cm, it has no squares. Twelve-sided dice are used and the coaches have a deck with spectacular plays.&amp;#10;A purely sporty, fast and spectacular game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
